title: OMG LOL! David Duke (yes, THAT David Duke) all but endorses Keith Ellison for DNC Chair
text:
OMG LOL! David Duke (yes, THAT David Duke) all but endorses Keith Ellison for DNC Chair Posted at 9:42 am on February 13, 2017 by Sam J.   
Oh man, the DNC is SUCH a mess. 
What with Debbie Wasserman Schultz getting the boot for “assisting” Hillary with the nomination to Donna Brazile (who also “assisted” Hillary and got the boot from CNN), it would seem they have a real problem. 
Luckily (for Democrats) the DNC is working on electing a new DNC chair … Running for DNC Chair. pic.twitter.com/bU8SlJeEkh 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 12, 2017 
Plenty of candidates running, including Keith Ellison, who was incidentally the first Muslim to be elected to the U.S. Congress. Trending Kellyanne Conway has the BEST answer in defense of Melania Trump 
Seems Keith has a “fan”: Keith Ellison, Sally Boynton Brown or Jehmu Greene would all be excellent choices – I really like Keith though… I mean, at least he knows. https://t.co/jXQK1CJEie 
— David Duke (@DrDavidDuke) February 12, 2017 
Ummm. 
David Duke says he “really likes” Keith Ellison. 
Not just likes him … REALLY likes him. 
That’s sort of an endorsement, right? I expect these endorsements to be covered extensively by the media. https://t.co/kKs5VoCvVd 
— Amanda Prestigiacomo (@AmandaPresto) February 13, 2017 
When will Ellison disavow this? Remember how mad the Democrats got when Duke praised Trump? 
Ha!
